1. *Lagao* je svima da ide u Å¡kolu. (He lied to everyone that he was going to school.) 
2. Ona je bila u pravu, ali on se *lagao*. (She was right, but he was lying.)
3. *Lagala* je njegova najbolja prijateljica. (His best friend was lying.)
